snippet.title: Slicks 'n Slide gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Slicks 'n Slide, Dos PC game produced by Timo Kauppinen in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/slicks-n-slide/4314/
Checking out a few tracks in this old school top down racing game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Death Rally - https://youtu.be/K9y0hPDlnYw
Super Karts - https://youtu.be/Oucev9oJ5Uo
Sega Rally - https://youtu.be/P-d_uvZSWEA
